The dining room in the hotel is the Dockside Restaurant which offers a fine menu for breakfast, lunch, and dinner.	The Dockside Restaurant in the hotel is superb, and we ended up eating there twice for dinner.	The hotel's bar and restaurant were both very nice, offered good food and beverages.	The event I attended had a lunch and reception in the restaurant and the food was fantastic.	The service from employees is always professional and courteous, the room is extremely clean, the restaurant food is good and the view is impeccable.